description: Nexus是一个强大的Maven仓库管理器，提供内部仓库的维护和外部仓库的访问的功能，可以帮助开发者建立Maven私服加速Maven构建，部署第三方构件，提高稳定性。
description_en: Nexus is a powerful Maven repository manager that provides internal repository maintenance and access to external repositories. It helps developers build Maven private services to accelerate Maven builds, deploy third-party artifacts, and improve stability.
